-- MOVES-SCIO Capital LLC appoints two directors
-- 
-- Fri Oct 03, 2014 07:52AM EDT
-- None



Oct 3 (Reuters) - London-based structured credit fund manager SCIO Capital LLC said it appointed two new directors.

Barry Lucassen joined SCIO's portfolio management team and will report to Eric Eastlund, head of analytics. Prior to this, Lucassen worked with investment management firm Aeris Capital AG, where he assisted the chief investment officer with asset allocation and was responsible for the firm's trading for six years.